{"tid":784673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】Wall Street Journal整咗個4分鐘短片，講解新疆集中營嘅現況","createTime":"2018-08-18T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T03:31:26.000Z","uid":131691,"like":103,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"15022a371e0ea4c87dee807d6a185be45a9a3534","tid":784673,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"Video: <a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/video/life-inside-china-re-education-camps/23B07DC7-76DC-4180-8033-20942D501BFF.html?mod=trending_now_video_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fvideo%2Flife-inside-china-re-education-camps%2F23B07DC7-76DC-4180-8033-20942D501BFF.html%3Fmod%3Dtrending_now_video_1&d=L%2Figdpc0Sp2N%2B2IKSq6yC7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3cc2106d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/video/life-inside-china-re-education-camps/23B07DC7-76DC-4180-8033-20942D501BFF.html?mod=trending_now_video_1</a><br />\n&ldquo;Life Inside China's 'Re-Education' Camps&rdquo;<br />\n真心癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5am起身<br />\n唱2-4小時強迫唱紅歌<br />\n逼睇維穩電影，政治宣傳電影<br />\n被人盤問：「呢個世界冇神，點解你有宗教信仰？」<br />\n幾廿人住一間細房，廁所都係嗰間房裏面<br />\n一日淨係畀食一個椰菜<br />\n唔畀講嘢<br />\n有個仲話畀人綁咗喺張鐵凳到幾日，閉關<br />\n幾乎每一個被訪問嘅中國境外維吾爾族人都有至少一個朋友或親人被消失<br />\n<br />\n依家仲有消息話啲集中營（中國叫佢哋做「教育營」）擴建緊<br />\n我屌<br />\n中囯呢個鬼國幾時瓦解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c99a899f9b78af566a1c9bcb66835cb63a6973","tid":784673,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ceaf27303a19747ce6d0c92630f704eb4be9c30","tid":784673,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj